'''''Challenge'' 35''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[1988]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including two adventures for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The articles were called "[[Team Recovery]]" and "[[The H-Wing Strike Fighter]]," and both were written by [[James B. King]].

